          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "A run takes us on the tour. Weaving forrest pathways set us up for a dune ridge line board walk that indicates the restaurant and chalets. We cut back via the inland lake. A small crocodile runs for the water and we run for our lives. ",
